title: The Warriors Take Game 2 in Blowout Win | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja discuss the first two games of the NBA Finals series between the Warriors and Celtics, including the Warriors' collapse in Game 1 and their blowout win in Game 2.
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Producer: Sasha Ashall
